data.title: Princess Marie of Baden, Princess of Leiningen
data.meta_description: Princess Marie of Baden was the third daughter and seventh child of Leopold, Grand Duke of Baden (1790–1852) and his wife Princess Sophie of Sweden (1801–65). She was Princess of Leiningen through her marriage with Ernst Leopold, 4th Prince of Leiningen.
